  itemName: Strawberry
  itemDescription: A pack of sweet, bright red berries. They are delicious and make
    you feel happy, but they will rot very quickly if you don't eat them soon.
  itemType: 2
  impactValue: 15
  educationalTip: Fresh berries are tasty and healthy, but they spoil in just a few
    days. In a survival situation, eat your fresh food immediately and save the canned
    food for later since it lasts much longer.
